DEMO EXCEL FILE: RECIPE PERFORMANCE ANALYSIS
==========================================

SHEET 1: Recipe Data
- Recipe success rates and attempt counts
- Difficulty ratings and time tracking
- Student feedback scores
- Modification frequency analysis

SHEET 2: Performance Dashboard
- Success rate trends over time
- Difficulty vs. success rate correlation
- Most/least successful recipes
- Student feedback analysis

SHEET 3: Recommendations
- Recipes needing curriculum updates
- Difficulty level adjustments
- Time allocation recommendations
- Student support suggestions

FORMULAS INCLUDED:
- =AVERAGE(SuccessRate) for overall performance
- =COUNTIF(Difficulty,"Hard") for difficulty distribution
- =VLOOKUP for recipe details
- Pivot tables for trend analysis

This Excel file would contain interactive charts,
conditional formatting, and advanced formulas for
comprehensive recipe performance analysis.
